name: BeaconProxyInitializable
description: This contract implements a proxy that gets the implementation address for each call from an {UpgradeableBeacon}. The beacon address is stored in storage slot `uint256(keccak256('eip1967.proxy.beacon')) - 1`, so that it doesn't conflict with the storage layout of the implementation behind the proxy. _Available since v3.4._.
